# Keep the build context small and the image clean: exclude VCS metadata,
# virtualenvs, build/test artifacts, the deployment scaffolding (compose/nginx/
# CI), and any local secrets/state. The Dockerfile copies only pyproject.toml,
# README.md, LICENSE, and the tao_sentinel package, so nothing here is needed to
# build the wheel.
.git
venv*
build/
*.egg-info
tests/
.github/
deploy/
sentinel.yaml
__pycache__
*.pyc
.review*
nohup.out
